        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-cursor&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;为进一步提升海外终端管理系统使用体验，我们将收集各位使用SalesforceAPP的手机品牌及对应型号。信息收集后，我们将进行系统性能优化，最大程度改善收集APP端的操作体验。感谢各位支持。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To further enhance the user experience of the overseas terminal management system, we will collect the mobile phone brands and corresponding models of those using the Salesforce APP. After gathering the information, we will proceed with system performance optimization to maximize the improvement of the operational experience on the APP side. Thank you for your support.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
